Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.63,0:00:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou ser o próximo representante conforme planejado.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.91,0:00:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu me opomo.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.34,0:00:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Clon de Ochiai.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.85,0:00:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Há quanto tempo você está aí?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.77,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx65}...{\r}Como ousa—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.59,0:00:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aguarde!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.37,0:01:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Está feito.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.22,0:01:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.02,0:01:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Altere o curso de Sidonia para o sistema estelar Lem.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.32,0:01:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Como desejar.
