Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.68,0:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,O monstro é um Gauna!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dentro de Sidonia, Gauna!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.10,DefaultAlt,,0,0,0,,Dentro de Sidonia, Gauna!
