Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:36.25,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se este mundo estiver condenado à ruína,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:36.25,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]aa kuchiteku sekai naraba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:39.75,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se minha vida estiver em perigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:39.75,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]chiriyuku sadame naraba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:45.34,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então por que eu deveria viver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:45.34,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]nani wo shinjite ikireba ii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:51.05,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se não tivesse conhecido você,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:51.05,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]sou kimi to deawanakereba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:54.43,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então eu nunca teria sentido este sofrimento
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:54.43,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}arrancando meu coração
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:23:01.06,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}quebrando meu coração ao meio
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:23:01.06,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por não conhecer dor alguma
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:03.77,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}é uma requisição grosseira
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:03.77,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}no horizonte do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:05.23,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ecoando para
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:05.23,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ressoou durante a noite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.23,0:23:09.07,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}as alturas do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.23,0:23:09.07,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}um requeim inútil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.03,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}E até agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.03,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}mas ainda
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.70,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}neste mundo sem sentido
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.70,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]sagashiteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:16.16,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu busco
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:16.16,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}um agora diferente
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.12,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}para você
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.12,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o que é você
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:21.75,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Eu me lembro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:21.75,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}sosai shite ita yorokobi mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:25.46,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}do prazer de te conhecer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:25.46,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]kieteitta nukumori mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:29.72,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e a passagem do seu estar aqui
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:29.72,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu lembro tudo isso sim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.80,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}porque eu te amei
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.80,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]aishiteta kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:36.51,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Gelo cresce no meu coração
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:36.51,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}mar de lágrimas que se estende
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:40.23,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}sobre as feridas dentro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:40.23,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]mune ni nokoru kizuato mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:44.61,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}eu levarei tudo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:44.61,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]nee zenbu kakaeteyuku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:51.66,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}e caminhe pelo meu caminho
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:51.66,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}seguindo este caminho
